---
title: Crispy Chicken Gyozas with Yellow Thai Style Peanut Stir-Fry
description: Pronounced gee-oh-zuh, you can find these delicious Japanese style dumplings filled with a mixture of minced meat and/or veg, but these ones are stuffed with chicken! Our Crispy Chicken Gyozas are oven-baked for extra crispiness and served atop a fragrant Thai style stir-fry.
